To anyone getting the "type 'Null' is not a subtype of type 'DatabaseNote' error, around 21:29:00

Change 
_note = snapshot.data as DatabaseNote;

to
_note = snapshot.data as DatabaseNote?;

The nullable question mark operator is important

if someone has an error at https://youtu.be/VPvVD8t02U8?t=40829 - 11.20.29, i fixed that with these:
In main.dart, starting from 38 line, use this for now

Future.delayed(Duration.zero, (() {
                  Navigator.push(
                      context,
                      MaterialPageRoute(
                        builder: (context) => const VerifyEmailView(),
                      ));
                }));.

